<plot>John Silliphant and Mark Peters found that ordinary people on either side of the Indo-Pak border have warm feelings for one another, with kids expressing the strongest feelings of friendship. Gathering letters across India and Pakistan, the two draw increasing amounts of volunteer energy, media attention, and support as they move towards a historic rock concert on the international border.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?321642</url></doc>
